Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Dubious poll results
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040h3r4
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 30 Sep 1979
Doubt cast on polls which give widely differing results of President Carter's standing with the general voter. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less